701554f-a.title: Bronx: Olmstead Avenue - St. Raymond Avenue
701554f-a.text:
Olmstead Avenue, at St. Raymond Avenue (vantage-point).
The view is northeastward toward E. Tremont Avenue, across the
area which will become part of the model housing development
to be erected by the Metropolitan Life IIisurance Company.
April 10, 1938
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

701753f-a.title: Bronx: St. Raymond's Avenue - Olmstead Avenue
701753f-a.text:
St. Raymond Avenue, north side, east from Olmstead Avenue.
The three-story brick buildint is the service building of the
Bronx Gas and Electric Company, at Odell Street.
April 10, 1938
P. L. Sperr
